OL,3,CMan dies on Pen y Fan while taking
OL,4,Cpart in endurance event
OL,6,FA man has died while participating in
OL,7,Fan endurance event on South Wales'
OL,8,Fhighest peak.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to Pen
OL,11,Fy Fan, in the Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,12,FNational Park, as known as the Brecon
OL,13,FBeacons, at around 11am on Saturday.
OL,15,FThe 68-year-old man was participating
OL,16,Fin a race organised by Avalanche
OL,17,FEndurance Events (AEE), which allows
OL,18,Fpeople from "all walks of life" to
OL,19,Ftake part in the Fan Dance, an
OL,20,Fendurance event used in the Special
OL,21,FForces selection process.
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@_O]
