OL,3,CMan dies on Pen y Fan while taking
OL,4,Cpart in endurance event
OL,6,FThe Fan Dance requires candidates to
OL,7,Fcomplete a 15-mile (24km) course up
OL,8,Fand around the 2,907ft (886m) peak
OL,9,Fcarrying a 35lb (16kg) pack.
OL,11,FA spokesman for Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "Dyfed-Powys Police received a
OL,13,Fcall following welfare concerns for a
OL,14,Fmale on Pen y Fan, Brecon, at around
OL,15,F11am on Saturday July 4.
OL,17,F"Officers attended alongside Mountain
OL,18,FRescue and the Ambulance Service.
OL,20,F"Sadly, the 68-year-old man passed
OL,21,Faway.
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@AOU|D@AOU
