OL,3,CMan dies on Pen y Fan while taking
OL,4,Cpart in endurance event
OL,6,F"His next of kin are aware and his
OL,7,Fdeath is not being treated as
OL,8,Fsuspicious.
OL,10,F"HM Coroner have been advised and
OL,11,Fofficers will continue to assist them
OL,12,Fwith their investigation."
OL,14,FAEE founder Ken Jones said in a
OL,15,Fstatement on Tuesday: "This message is
OL,16,Fto share news that AEE experienced a
OL,17,Ffatality during the Fan Dance Race
OL,18,FSeries event on Saturday July 4 2026.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@ZO]wD@WOU
