OL,3,CMan dies on Pen y Fan while taking
OL,4,Cpart in endurance event
OL,6,F"At this immediate time our focus and
OL,7,Fthoughts are with the family,
OL,8,Ftherefore AEE nor I as the march
OL,9,Fdirector will issue any further press
OL,10,Frelease until the family is in
OL,11,Fpossession of the full timeline of
OL,12,Fevents and approve any further
OL,13,Fmessaging.
OL,15,F"Our team is working on this at the
OL,16,Ftime of posting.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
