OL,3,CMan dies on Pen y Fan while taking
OL,4,Cpart in endurance event
OL,6,F"I wish to express my thanks to the
OL,7,FAir Ambulance Service, Brecon Mountain
OL,8,FRescue Team, and AEE's Mountain Safety
OL,9,FTeam for their swift response and
OL,10,Fprofessionalism.
OL,12,F"Also, our thanks to those event
OL,13,Fpatrons whose professional response
OL,14,Falso helped manage this challenging,
OL,15,Fsignificant event."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@SO]
